'Yan majalisar Welsh suna damuwa da cewa za a iya gano su a matsayin Muppets
Da dama daga cikin 'yan majalisar sun nuna bacin ran su game da shawarar da aka gabatar na sauya mukaminsa na MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan gardama ta taso ne bayan shirin canza sunan majalisar zuwa majalisar Welsh.
'Yan majalisa daga dukkan bangarorin siyasa daban-daban sun nuna damuwarsu cewa wannan matakin zai zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisar majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta damu da cewa MWP ya shiga Twp ko Pwp.
Ga wadanda ba Welsh ba: A cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa, kuma pwp yana nufin fasiki.
Wani memba na majalisar Plaid Cymru ya ce duk jam'iyyarsa ba ta da kyau kuma ta gabatar da wasu hanyoyi.
A gefe guda, wani memba na Welsh mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce kungiyarsa ta kasance obert a gaban canjin sunan, amma kuma ya yi sharhi cewa akwai bambanci kaɗan tsakanin kalmar MWP da Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, dole ne a ce ana furta harafin w a cikin Welsh kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a Turanci na Yorkshire.
A cewar kwamitin majalisar da ke da alhakin tsara tsarin doka don gabatar da canje-canjen sunaye: Yanke shawara na ƙarshe game da kowane cancantar kiran membobin majalisar zai kasance a hannun membobin kansu. 
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba Majalisar Wales dukkan ikon canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya fitar da sakamakon binciken jama'a kan shawarwarin, tare da tallafi mai yawa don sunan majalisa ya canza zuwa Welsh Parliament.
Dangane da taken membobin majalisar, kodayake kwamitin ya zaɓi Membobin majalisar Welsh ko WPM, zaɓin MWP shine wanda ya sami mafi yawan tallafi a cikin shawarwarin jama'a.
A bayyane yake, 'yan majalisar suna ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin daban-daban, amma ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama abin damuwa ga Shugaban Majalisar, Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da daftarin doka kan canje-canje a cikin makonni.
Dokar sake fasalin za ta haɗa da wasu canje-canje da suka shafi aikin majalisa, kamar su ka'idoji game da rashin cancantar membobinta da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisa za su yi zaɓe na ƙarshe a kan sunayensu a lokacin muhawara da ta shafi doka.
