Masana sun ce, ficewar mai gabatar da shirin na This Morning, daya daga cikin taurari mafi samun riba a Burtaniya, na iya kashe kamfanin miliyoyin saboda babban jarin da aka yi a kayayyaki, daga matashin kai da kyandirori zuwa tufafi da tufafi na gida, da kuma yiwuwar jinkiri a fitarwa.
