Fiye da masu kallo miliyan 20 sun kalli jawabin Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli wani shaida mai ban mamaki da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis, wanda ya nuna cewa, wanda ake zargi da laifin cin zarafin mata da maza, wato Brett Kavanaugh, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, sun yi zargin cewa, an yi lalata da su a shekarun 1980s.
A halin yanzu, rashin daidaito na siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da tashoshin da ke dakatar da shirye-shiryen Juma'a saboda wani juyi na ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na zargi na mako guda.
A wata sanarwa da ta aika wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa, Ford ta bayyana cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin ya yi mata fyade a lokacin wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da aka yi, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa wannan ba abin da ya faru ba ne.
A cewar Nielsen, kimanin mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan shirin a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin masu kallo na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanan masu sauraro ba nan take daga wasu tashoshin da suka watsa wannan shaidar, kamar PBS, C-SPAN, ko Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da matsala wajen ƙididdige mutanen da suke kallon shi daga ofishinsa.
Idan aka sa shi a cikin hangen nesa, wannan yana kama da kallon wasan kwallon kafa ko kuma na Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda shugabannin ra'ayoyin jama'a suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya kasance tashar da ta fi samun yawan masu sauraro, inda ta samu kimanin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin rana guda, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ita ce ta biyu a jerin da ke da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94 MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Mutane sun ci gaba da son saƙon bayan an ba da shaida.
Flake ya kasance babban mutum a wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin ɗan Republican mai tsaka-tsaka ya fitar da sanarwa cewa za su zaɓe a kan Kavanaugh, Flake ya shiga cikin kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar ranar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka kama shi yayin da yake ƙoƙarin hawa hawa don zuwa wani kallo na Kwamitin Harkokin Shari'a.
Flake ya yi minti da dama da ido a yayin da aka sake dawowa a kan talabijin a CNN.
"Ga ni nan a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
