LeBron zai buga wa Lakers wasa a San Diego ranar Lahadi
Jiran da ake yi ya kusan karewa ga magoya bayan da suke son ganin LeBron James ya buga wasan farko da Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta farko da Denver Nuggets a San Diego ranar Lahadi.
Amma har yanzu ba a tantance yawan minti da za ta yi ba.
"Za su kasance fiye da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mike Trudell, dan jaridar Lakers, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai iya buga wasan na 'yan mintuna.
Bayan an gama wasannin a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na sake buga wa Lakers wasanni shida a kakar wasan bana.
"Ba na bukatar wasan farko a wannan lokaci na rayuwata don in kasance a shirye", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara wani gangami na ayyukan yakin neman zabe a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar wuraren da ake son masu goyon baya, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran a kada kuri'ar tabbatar da takararsa a kotun koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon da ke da shi a majalisar dokoki a lokacin da za a gudanar da zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai kasance a wannan maraice kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon shi ta yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne da karfe 7 na yamma a yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Ana iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar bidiyo kai tsaye ta YouTube a wannan hanyar.
Trump zai yi jawabi a gaban kotun da za a yi wa wanda ya zama dan takarar a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya fuskanci tashin hankali saboda zargin da ake masa na cin zarafin mata, yayin da ake jiran zaben da za a yi a majalisar dattijai don tabbatar da shi, kuma hukumar FBI za ta ci gaba da bincike a kan lamarin.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron na neman 'yancin kai shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman yin zabe a watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
A sakamakon haka, taron yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump na mako mai zuwa, za a shirya shi ne domin karfafa gwiwar 'yan sa kai da magoya bayan sa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan kujerun da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
"Sarrafa Majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban, don haka zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yadda zai iya, yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa, kamar yadda kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters ya ruwaito.
Taron na yau da dare, wanda aka shirya a filin wasa na Wesbanco Arena, Wheeling, zai iya tara masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia News Metro.
A ranar Asabar, za a yi ziyarar Trump ta biyu a West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe kashi 40 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar Sanata na Jamhuriyar Republican daga West Virginia, wanda ke samun mummunan sakamako a zaben fidda gwani.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa a cikin zaɓe", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka ta nuna burinta na ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman wasa uku, wasan tara-tara na yammacin Asabar mai yiwuwa shine abin da Ryder Cup ke buƙata.
Matsayin jujjuyawar juzu'i wata ma'anar wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ce da aka ƙirƙira, wanda 'yan wasa suka yi imani da gaske, musamman a gasa kamar wannan.
To, wane bangare ne a halin yanzu ke da kyakkyawan yanayi?
"Suna da tazarar maki shida kuma yanzu ta zama hudu, don haka ina ganin muna cikin wani ɗan ƙaramin ci gaba", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake tafiya a ƙarshen ranar.
A bayyane yake cewa Turai tana da fifiko, da maki huɗu a gaba, da kuma maki goma sha biyu a wasa.
