Tauraron wasan kwaikwayon "Game of Thrones" Kit Harington ya yi zargin cewa yana da wata irin mugun hali na namiji
Kit Harington an san shi da yin wasan kwaikwayo na Swordman Jon Snow a cikin HBO's wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na tsufa na tsufa.
Duk da haka, mai wasan kwaikwayo, mai shekaru 31, ya soki stereotype na jarumi mai karfi, yana mai cewa waɗannan ayyukan suna nuna cewa samari suna ganin cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don a girmama su.
A cikin wata hira da jaridar Culture ta The Sunday Times, Kit ya ce yana ganin "wani abu ya tafi daidai ba daidai ba" kuma yana tambayar kansa yadda za a magance matsalar mazaje masu guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan tare da 'yar wasan kwaikwayo na "Game of Thrones" Rose Leslie, wanda yake da shekara 31, ya yarda cewa yana da ƙarfin zuciya don magance wannan matsala.
"A gare ni, ina mamakin inda muka yi kuskure game da namiji", in ji shi.
Menene muka koya wa mutane a lokacin da suke tasowa dangane da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?
A cewar Kit, talabijin na iya daukar wani bangare na alhakin karuwar maza da ke da illa saboda halayyarsu ta maza.
Ya kara da cewa: "Abin da aka haifa da abin da aka samu?
Menene ake nunawa a talabijin da kuma a kan tituna da ya sa yara maza suke jin cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan bangare na namiji?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a zamaninmu: yaya za mu canza wannan?
Domin babu shakka akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba da aka yi wa samari.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones ba lokacin da aka shirya wasan karshe na wasan kwaikwayon don bazara mai zuwa, duk da cewa yana da yawa daga fadace-fadace da dawakai.
Daga Nuwamba, Kit zai yi rawar gani a wasan kwaikwayo na Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai shirya fina-finai da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɓarawo ne.
Mai wasan kwaikwayo kwanan nan ya bayyana cewa sanin abokin tarayya Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya ba shi Game da Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a cikin wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata gaba", in ji shi.
Rose ta taka rawar Ygritte, ƙaunataccen Kit, Jon Snow, a cikin jerin almara mai nasara na Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gidan Leslie na iyali, a Scotland.
Cutar HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar masu cutar a kashi 14 cikin dari
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Akwai mutane fiye da 820,000 da cutar ta shafa a kasar, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an ba da rahoton sabbin maganganu 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtukan da ake samu a yau, ana samunsu ne ta hanyar jima'i, ba kamar yadda ake samunsu a dā ba.
A dā, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri a wasu yankuna na ƙasar Sin ta wajen karɓan jini da yake ɗauke da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV saboda wannan dalili ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutum 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An ba da izinin yin luwadi a China a 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga LGBT jama'a ya zama ruwan dare.
Ganin dabi'un kasar da suka dace, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da ke yin luwadi da mata za su yi aure.
Mutane da yawa suna kamuwa da cututtuka ta wurin yin lalata.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin HIV ga kowa a kasar Sin a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance cutar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikacin jami'ar ta ya leaked data na Republican Sanata da kuma dismantles "dangerous rudu" da kuma "dabaru na mãkirci"
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka, Maxine Waters, ta yi ikirarin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattawa uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yar'uwar Democrat ta Los Angeles ta yi ikirarin cewa masu sukar da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na' yan tsakiya ne suka sa suka yi wannan ikirarin.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya da ƙara ƙazantar ƙarya", Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a kan Twitter.
An yi zargin cewa bayanan da aka wallafa sun hada da adireshin da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu biyu na Utah.
Bayanin ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis kuma wani da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa shi a Capitol yayin zaman kwamitin majalisar dattawa kan zargin cin zarafin mata da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayanin ya fito ne bayan da 'yan majalisar dattawa uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke nuna asalin abubuwan da aka buga yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma yana bayyana bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, Capitol ya yi zargin.
Waters ya ci gaba da cewa, "Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe, karya ne kuma ƙarya ce kawai".
"Wanda ya zama ma'aikacina, wanda aka yi wa zargin karya da kuma zamba, ba shi da alhakin yadda aka sako bayanan.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe, karya ne gaba daya kuma zage-zage ne".
Bayanin Waters ya jawo suka a kan layi, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana cike da fushi", Fleischer ya rubuta.
"Wannan ya nuna ba shi da halin da zai yi aiki a Majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da wani abin da bai yi ba, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Kada ka nuna kanka mai ƙalubalantar.
Bai kamata ya yi shakkar abin da mai zargin yake nufi ba.
Ya kamata ya kasance mai natsuwa da kuma natsuwa".
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa ya kwatanta yadda Waters ya yi da yadda 'yan Democrat suka soki Alkali Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zarge shi da cewa ya yi fushi sosai a zaman da aka yi ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman ya tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Matsayi idan gaskiya ne", ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da hukumomi da hukumomin tsaro masu dacewa game da wadannan maganganun zamba.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu laifin", in ji shi, "kuma za a hukunta su bisa dukkan ayyukan da suka aikata da kuma cutar da kowane ma'aikacina".
