Mene ne bikin 'yan kasa na duniya? Shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A yau Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin Global Citizen Festival, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara, wanda ke gabatar da wani shiri mai ban mamaki na taurari, waɗanda ke yin irin wannan manufa mai ban mamaki: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatar mutane sun taru a filin Great Lawn na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da burin duniya na bikin na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci a duniya kafin 2030.
Bikin Baƙin Duniya, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ɓangare ne na Gidajen Talauci na Duniya, ƙungiyar ba da agaji ta duniya da ke fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar ƙara yawan mutanen da ke taimakawa wajen yaƙi da talauci.
Don karɓar tikiti kyauta don taron (duk wanda yake so ya biya kuɗin shiga VIP), masu halarta dole ne su yi jerin ayyuka ko "ayyuka", kamar su ba da agaji, aika imel zuwa shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya, ko duk wani aiki don wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Wane ci gaba ne Global Citizen ya samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage kafin ya kai ga wannan burin?
Tunanin bai wa mutane kyauta kyauta kyauta hanya ce mai kyau don shawo kan su don neman kira zuwa aiki ko kuma kawai wani lamari ne na abin da muke kira "clictivism" (mutane suna tunanin cewa yana da bambanci don sanya hannu kan takardar neman layi ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta yi ikirarin cewa ta yi rikodin sama da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayanta, wanda ya taimaka wajen cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ta ce wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen karfafa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 37, wanda zai shafi rayuwar mutane sama da miliyan 2,250 kafin shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da sanarwar da aka samu daga ayyukanta, wanda ya riga ya biya ko ya karɓi dala biliyan 10 aƙalla.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, a yanzu haka, asusun da aka kare sun yi tasiri kai tsaye ga kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawurran sun hada da Gidauniyar The Power of Nutrition, wata ƙungiya ce ta masu saka jari da masu ba da gudummawa da ke Burtaniya, wanda ke yin alƙawarin "taimaka wa yara su girma yadda ya kamata" kuma ya yi alkawarin aika da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen magance matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a Ruwanda bayan karɓar fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Global Citizens.
"Godiya ga goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da membobin Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya juya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihin tarihi", in ji Jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ga taron jama'a a wani wasan kwaikwayo na rayuwa a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
