Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin gina sabuwar intanet don yin gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da kuma Google.
Aikin karshe na mashahurin fasahar, Inrupt, kamfani ne da aka gina akan dandalin bude tushen Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid Platform yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda zasu iya samun damar zuwa wasu bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Kamfanin Fast, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa burin Inrupt na ɓoye shi ne " mamaye duniya ".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfanin da ke fitowa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha na dandamali na Solid don bawa masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar "ɗakin ajiyar bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da aka tsara, kalanda, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify, duk suna samuwa a cikin wani browser a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da mahimmanci na ajiyar bayanan sirri na sirri shi ne cewa mai amfani ne wanda ya yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Babban Jami'in Gudanarwa na kamfanin, John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya haɗa albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da ta dace don dandamali na Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu yana da Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro wanda IBM ya saya, wasu masu haɓaka ƙira da aka ba su izini don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummomin masu ba da agaji.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar kayan aikin da ke kan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce babu wani a cikin tawagarsa da ke tattaunawa da "Facebook da Google kan ko ya kamata a kawo sauyi mai zurfi inda duk tsarin kasuwancin zai zama banza a cikin dare.
"Ba ma tambayar su izini".
A cikin wani rubutu a ranar Asabar a Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "Inrupt's mission is to provide commercial power and an ecosystem to help protect the integrity and quality of the new web integrated into the Solid platform".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya fasalin yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa Gidan yanar gizo na Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
