Magoya bayan MMMA da suka kwana a kan Bellator 206 sun ga Peppa Pig a wurin
Ka yi tunanin cewa za ka yi barci da daddare don ka kalli wasan Bellator 206, amma a hana ka ganin wasan da ya fi muhimmanci a wasan.
San Jose ta sanarwa ta ƙunshi wasanni 13, ciki har da shida daga cikin manyan katunan kuma za a iya ganin su a cikin dare a Birtaniya a Channel 5.
A karfe 6:00 na safe, yayin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin fuskantar juna, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka canza shirin zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun nuna ba'a don sun kasance a farke har zuwa safiya don kallon gwagwarmaya.
Wani mai bin Twitter ya bayyana sauya fasalin zane-zane a matsayin "wani irin ciwon amai".
