Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji kansa inferior game da jima'i
Dan tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa ya fi sauran mutane saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don cin nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 24 ya bayyana cewa bai gane ba har sai da ya je makarantar sakandare cewa ba kowa bane kamarsa.
A shirin Radio 4 na Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce yana magana ne game da haƙƙin 'yan luwadi don ba da 'fatar zuciya' ga wasu mutane.
Ya kuma ce kasancewarsa uba ya rage mahimmancin lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young, wadda ta saba da wannan shirin, ta yi wata huɗu a duniya ba tare da samun lafiya ba.
Daley, wanda ya bayyana a matsayin mai haɗari a cikin shirin farko na Laverne, ya ce yana jin "ƙananan" fiye da sauran mutane saboda "ba a yarda da zamantakewa kamar yara maza da mata ba".
Ta ce, "A yau, waɗannan jin cewa na fi kowa da kuma banbanci, sun kasance ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni iko da ƙarfin da zan yi nasara".
Ta so ta tabbatar da cewa ita ce "wani abu", in ji ta, don kada ta ba da kunya ga kowa lokacin da ta gano ta jima'i.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics mai lambar tagulla sau biyu ya zama babban mai gabatar da motsi na LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da hotonsa a Wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su yanke hukuncin nuna luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne saboda ya ji cewa ya yi sa'a da ya sami damar yin rayuwa a fili ba tare da wani abin da ya same shi ba, kuma yana son ya ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya bayyana cewa ya ƙaunaci wani mutum, mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka, Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a 2013, "ya kama shi da mamaki".
A shekarar da ta gabata, Daley ta auri wani dan wasan da ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, amma ta ce bambancin shekarun ba ta taba zama matsala ba.
A cewarsa, idan ka sha wahala a lokacin da kake matashi (ta shiga wasannin Olympics na farko lokacin tana da shekara 14 kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga cutar kansa shekaru uku bayan haka), yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunta wanda ya sami irin wannan tashin hankali da tashin hankali.
Ma'auratan sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni na wani yaro wanda suka sa wa suna Robert Ray Black-Daley. A cewar Daley, "duk hangen nesan su" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a shekarar da ta gabata, duk abin da nake bukata shi ne in lashe zinaren Olympics", in ji shi.
"Akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Gwarzon zinare na a gasar Olympics na shi ne Robbie".
An kira ɗansa kamar mahaifinsa, Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 saboda cutar kansa.
