A wani mummunan Mickelson ya gabatar da Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan da ya fi kowa a tarihi a ranar Lahadi, a wasan da ya buga na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup, amma dole ne ya sauya yanayin jikinsa idan ba ya son ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda zai shiga cikin taron shekara-shekara don buga rikodin a karo na 12, an gabatar da shi ne daga kyaftin Jim Furyk don yanayin "fourballs" da "fourfoursomes" a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya saba a Amurka, mai nasara a manyan wasanni biyar ya raba lokacinsa tsakanin yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma aiki a wasan da yake a fagen, da fatan gyara abin da ke cutar da shi.
Bai taɓa yin direbobin kai tsaye ba, har ma a lokacin da ya fi ƙwarewa a cikin aikinsa, amma ɗan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shine mafi kyawun zaɓi ba don mawuyacin yanayin Le Golf National, inda dogon rough yakan hukunta bugun da ya ɓace.
Kuma idan tarihinsa bai isa ya ba da tsoro ba, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, zai fuskanci mai nasara a gasar Open British Francesco Molinari, wanda ya haɗu da rookie Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amurka, wadanda suka sha kashi hudu a raga a wasannin da suka buga guda 12, suka fara da karfi, to wasan Mickelson zai iya zama na karshe.
Furyk ya nuna amincewarsa ga wannan mutumin, ba tare da iya gaya masa wani abu ba.
"Ya fahimci matsayinsa a ranar, ya buga ni a baya kuma ya kewaye ni da hannunsa yana gaya mini cewa zai kasance a shirye gobe", in ji Furyk.
"Yana da gaba gaɗi sosai.
Gidan wasan kwaikwayo ne kuma ya taimaka wa waɗannan ƙungiyoyin a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin cewa zai yi wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin ƙarin, amma wannan ita ce hanyar da nake horarwa kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da muke tunanin za mu ci gaba.
Yana son zama a wurin kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a matsayin wanda ya fi kowa yawan wasa a gasar Ryder Cup.
Zai iya nufin ƙarshen tseren Ryder Cup wanda bai daidaita da rikodin mutum ɗaya ba.
Mickelson ya sami nasara 18, ya sha kashi 20 kuma ya daidaita 7, duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya kawo abubuwa marasa amfani ga ƙungiyar.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ban dariya, mai ban dariya, yana son yin ba'a da mutane kuma babban abokin aiki ne ga ƙungiyar", in ji shi.
Ina tsammanin 'yan wasan matasa suna jin daɗin yin lalata da shi a wannan makon, abin da ya kasance abin kallo.
