Guguwar zafi ta bazara ta kara yawan cin abinci a gidajen giya da ke fama da matsalar rashin isasshen ruwan sha a Burtaniya, amma ta kara matsin lamba a gidajen abinci.
Bars da sarkar sanduna sun sami karuwar kashi 2.7% a cikin tallace-tallace a watan Yuli, amma cin abinci a gidajen cin abinci ya ragu da kashi 4.8%, kamar yadda ƙididdigar ta nuna.
Peter Martin, na kamfanin ba da shawara kan harkokin kudi na CGA, kamfanin da ya tattara bayanan, ya ce: "Ci gaba da samun rana da kuma halartar Ingila a gasar cin kofin duniya, wanda ya fi tsayi fiye da yadda aka yi tsammani, ya sa watan Yuli ya bi wani tsari kamar na Yuni, tare da karuwar 2.8% a cikin sanduna, sai dai a cikin gidajen cin abinci, waɗanda suka fi wahala.
Rashin ci da kashi 1.8 cikin dari a cikin gidajen cin abinci a watan Yuni ya kara muni a watan Yuli.
Bars da mashaya, wanda yawan shan giya ya jagoranci, sun sami sakamako mafi kyau, yayin da amfani a gidajen abinci ya ragu.
Gidan giya da ke ba da abinci ma sun sha wahala daga rana, kodayake ba ta kasance mai ban mamaki ba kamar yadda yake a gidajen abinci.
