Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jami'ai.
Saboda an katse sadarwa, rukunin ba da agaji ba su sami bayanai daga Donggala Regency ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu mafi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Cèlebes na Tsakiya, wanda ke gefen ƙarancin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Cèlebes, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin shekarar 2017.
Garin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ya mamaye fiye da kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Yankin, yanki ne na gwamnati wanda bai kai lardi ba, yana da kusan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Central Celebes, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a bakin tekun na gefen Cèlebes.
Palu da Donggala sun fuskanci tsunami da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar rage bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 kuma an samu wata mummunar guguwar tsunami a yammacin Donggala wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Kasar Indonesiya tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma a yawancin lokaci ana girgizar ƙasa.
A ƙasa an lissafa manyan girgizar asa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami da ta shafi kasashe 14 kuma ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Dubban mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta girgiza wani yanki a garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Sama da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabar tekun Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai girman mita 10 da ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai rauni ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, yayin da yawan jama'a suka tuna da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004 da suka mutu.
A wannan karon, babu tsunami, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu sakamakon gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: An yi jerin manyan girgizar kasa a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia wanda ya kashe mutane 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin da laifin cin zarafin mata
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mai neman takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, da laifin aikata mugunta.
Palin, mai shekaru 29, dan asalin Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi da zargin cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki da rahoton cin zarafin gida da kuma tsayayya da kamawa, a cewar wani rahoto da Alaska State Troopers ta buga a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata abokiyarta ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don yin rahoto game da laifukan da ake zargin ta yi, ta cire wayar ta.
An tsare Palin a cibiyar tsare tsare na Mat-Su, inda aka tsare shi tare da wani bashi mara kyau na dala 500, a cewar KTUU.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, lokacin da ya bayyana "ba laifi ba, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda yake bayyana, a cewar wannan tashar.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya zuwa gidan yari har zuwa shekara guda kuma ya biya tarar har zuwa dala 250,000.
Ana kuma tuhumar shi da laifin aji B, wanda zai iya jawo hukuncin kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017 an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa, Todd Palin hari.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi mata.
A yanzu haka, wannan shari'ar tana hannun Kotun Tsoffin Sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 aka tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata, da kuma yin katsalandan da ake zargi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, da kuma mallakar makami a yayin da yake cikin maye, dangane da lamarin.
Matar matarsa ta ce ta buge shi da hannu a fuska.
A shekara ta 2016, Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji saboda danganta halayyar ɗanta na tashin hankali da rikicewar rikice-rikice wanda ya samo asali daga hidimarsa a Iraki.
