Masu shigar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da kai harin New York hukuncin kisa na musamman
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa mai ban mamaki wanda ba a yi a jihar ba don wani laifi na tarayya tun daga 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ana zargin ya yi amfani da wata babbar motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke na West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan da kuma tayar da masu tafiya da kekuna a kan hanya a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a Kudancin New York.
Dukkan laifuffukan biyu na iya kai ga hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta zargi Saipov da laifin 22 wanda ya hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don amfanin aikata laifuka, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'ar Mafia, ban da laifin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "tsari da tunani mai zurfi" kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata a matsayin "ba shi da mutunci, mugunta da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asara ga iyalai da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cewar sanarwar da aka yi niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da kotu ta yanke hukuncin kisa a Kudancin New York.
Wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, an same shi da laifin kisan wasu dillalan miyagun kwayoyi, amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A ƙarshe an kashe hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York a 1953 don Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa saboda ƙulla makirci don yin leƙen asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Cold shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenbergs sun mutu a cikin kujera na lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
A cewar takardar da aka shigar, Saipov ya bayyana wa hukumomi cewa an yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don kai harin bayan ya ga bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce, ya kuma bukaci a saka tutar ISIS a cikin ɗakinsa a asibiti.
Ya amsa cewa ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare 'yancin jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun kasance "a fili sun yi nadama" da hukuncin da ake tuhumar.
"Bari mu yi la'akari da cewa yanke shawara don neman hukuncin kisa, maimakon karbar takardar da'awar da kuma ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar 'yanci ba, zai kawai tsawaita raunin da ya faru ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce ya kamata a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a matsayin wanda zai jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "taro da sojojin jama'a" a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron jam'iyyar Conservative.
Tsohon shugaban na UKIP ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su "ji matsin lamba daga masu ra'ayin Turai" lokacin da daya daga cikin mambobin majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ta jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin rikon kwarya Peter Bone ya fada a lokacin wani gangami a birnin Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta riga ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai idan Mista Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta na sasantawa tsakanin bangarorinta da suka rabu ya kara bayyana a lokacin da masu goyon bayan hadin kan suka fito a wani zanga-zanga na Brexit a birnin.
Firaministan kasar tana kokarin ganin ta ci gaba da shirin da ta yi na Chequers tsakanin hare-haren da magoya bayan ficewar Birtaniya daga kungiyar EU da kuma magoya bayan kungiyar tarayyar Turai.
'Yan kungiyar sun dage cewa zai cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da korafe-korafen da ake yi masa, kuma sun matsa wa masu ra'ayin gurguzu da masu ra'ayin ra'ayin Tmani da su zabi tsakanin shirinsa da kuma rudani.
Mista Bone ya ce a taron Solihull na Leave Means Leave cewa yana son ya soke alkawarin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a sanya Mista Farage a matsayin memba na majalisar Lords kuma ya kamata a ba shi alhakin yin shawarwari tare da Brussels.
'Idan ya kasance a cikin cajin, za mu kasance a waje,' in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu soke alkawarin Chequers".
Don bayyana takun sa ga EU, ya kara da cewa: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don bayi ba.
Muna son yin dokokinmu a kasarmu".
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da shawarwarin da ke cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun daga zaben 2016: "Ganin cewa jama'ar Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son zama a ciki gaba ɗaya ƙarya ne".
Tuni dai Andrea Jenkyns, mai goyon bayan Brexit, ta halarci wannan gangamin, inda ta bayyana wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina gaya muku, firaminista, ku saurari mutane".
"Hadin Chequers ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi zaɓe a kansa ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutukarmu, waɗanda su ne mutanen da ke fita zuwa titi kuma suka sa mu lashe zabe.
Ka bar alkawarin Chequers ka fara sauraro. "
A wata wasika da ta aike wa Mrs May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai Ministoci suna kiyaye aikinsu ne idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Mista Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa a taron na bukatar su ji matsin lamba idan suna son su janye shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan, yanzu, batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu (mutane) da kuma rukunin siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin yin karya ga Brexit kuma a yau muna nan don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari ba".
A cikin wani sako ga jama'a masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina son ku sa 'yan siyasa, da ke shirin janye Brexit, su ji matsin".
"Muna tattara dakarun jama'a daga wannan kasa da suka ba mu nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, masu cin gashin kai da kuma alfahari da Birtaniya".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ƙungiyar sun yi zanga-zanga a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a cikin gari.
Wasu masu fafutuka sun yi ta daga tutocin masu adawa da Brexit bayan da aka kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservative dariya kan matsalar tsaro da suka fuskanta a shafin yanar gizon jam'iyyar a farkon taron.
"Waɗannan su ne mutanen da suka gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da ake bukata da kuma duk wata fasaha don yarjejeniyar Kanada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da rikici, don cinikayya kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
"Wannan duk wani abin zamba ne.
Babu wani zaɓi na Brexit mai kyau", in ji shi.
Warren yana shirin duba yiwuwar tsayawa takara a matsayin shugaban kasa
'Yar'uwar Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta duba ko za ta iya tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa a ranar Asabar, 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat ta Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomarta a wani taron da aka yi a yammacin Massachusetts.
Warren, wanda ke yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, ya yi tseren sake zabensa a watan Nuwamba a kan wakilin jihar na GOP Geoff Diehl, wanda ya kasance mataimakin shugaban kamfen na Massachusetts na Trump a shekarar 2016.
An yi ta hasashen cewa Trump zai maye gurbinsa a shekara ta 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne karo na 36 na ganawa da masu jefa kuri'a a cikin tsarin taron budewa tun lokacin da Trump ya hau kujerar mulkin.
Wani daga cikin masu sauraronta ya tambaye ta ko tana da niyyar tsayawa takarar shugabancin kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ba ta aiki ba, kuma wannan ya haɗa da mace a kan shugabanci".
An kama mutum daya bisa laifin kisan Sims, na jami'ar LSU
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa sun kama wanda ake zargi da laifin harbin dan wasan kwando na LSU, Wayde Sims, a ranar Juma'a.
Rundunar 'yan sanda ta Baton Rouge ta sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a taron manema labarai na ET 11:00.
Sun wallafa wani faifan bidiyo na harbin ranar Juma'a kuma suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da ya yi harbin.
An harbe Sims, mai shekara 20, a kusa da harabar jami'ar Southern University da safiyar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya sami harbi a kai wanda a karshe ya kashe shi", in ji jami'in 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a ranar Asabar a kafofin watsa labarai na 247sports.
Wayde ya yi kokarin kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An tambayi Simpson kuma ya yarda da cewa ya kasance a wurin, yana da bindiga, kuma ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wani abin da ya faru ba kuma aka kai shi cikin ofishin 'yan sanda na gundumar East Baton.
Sims, dan wasan matasa mai tsayi 2 wanda ya girma a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 a cikin wasanni 10 a kakar wasa ta bara kuma yana da minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da kuma rebo 2.9 a kowane wasa.
