Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a raga a wasan da Giants suka buga da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi nasara da nasarar da suka yi a ranar Juma'a a Elite da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci wasan baya 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants nan da nan suka sami nasarar cin kwallaye biyu saboda kwallaye na Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun ɗaga matakin ƙungiyar su, amma daga baya, Dwyer ya dawo da Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita Dundee, sannan kuma Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya zira kwallaye biyu don tabbatar da nasararsa.
Wannan ne dai kashi na uku da Adam Keefe ya samu a kakar wasa ta bana a gasar Premier ta Ingila, bayan da suka doke Dundee da ci biyu a wasan farko da suka buga a Belfast ranar Juma'a.
Wannan shine karo na huɗu na kakar tsakanin ƙungiyoyin biyu kuma Giants sun ci wasannin uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara cin kwallo a minti na huɗu, a 3:35, daga taimakon Kendall McFaull. Minti huɗu daga baya, tare da taimakon David Rutherford, Beauvillier zai ninka ta gaba.
A lokacin wannan lokacin tashin hankali, Sullivan ya sake sanya ƙungiyar gida a wasan a minti 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya sauƙaƙa a minti 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da Giants a farkon lokacin hutu lokacin da ya ci gaba da raga na biyu a daren a ƙarshen farkon.
Teamungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma, Bouchard ya sake ba da gudummawa ga matakin su tare da babbar manufa a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar farko a wasan a ƙarshen kashi na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagarsa ta hanyar cin kwallo biyar a kusa da ƙarshen wasan.
Giants, wadanda suka yi rashin nasara a hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka gabata, suna gida a Milton Keynes kuma suna da wasa na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don ceton daruruwan fasinjoji daga jirgin da ya girgiza
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia ya zama jarumi bayan ya mutu don tabbatar da jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan fasinjoji ya sauka lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma da yawa sun bata bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Celebes a ranar Juma'a kuma ta haifar da tsunami.
Akwai girgizar kasa da yawa a yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin rugujen a garin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun tsere don ceton rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, mai shekara 21, ya ki ya bar wurinsa a kan hasumiyar kula da filin jirgin sama na Palu Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport.
Ya tsaya a wurinsa don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Flight 6321, wanda ke kan hanya a lokacin, zai iya tashi cikin aminci.
Bayan haka, sai ya fito daga hasumiyar da ke kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a lokacin da ya yi tunanin cewa zai faɗi.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Wani mai magana da yawun kamfanin Air Navigation, Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton rayuka da dama, kamar yadda Australia ta ABC News ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don mu kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, mun rasa shi da safe kafin helikofta ya isa birnin Palu.
"Wannan ya sa mu baƙin ciki sosai", in ji ta.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai, yayin da hukumar rage radadin bala'i ta sanar da cewa an takaita samun damar shiga biranen Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu saboda har yanzu akwai gawarwaki da yawa a karkashin kango kuma har yanzu akwai wasu da ba a samu damar shiga ba", in ji wakilin kamfanin Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Guguwar da ta kai tsawon mita shida ta mamaye garin Palu, inda za a yi jana'izar al'ummar garin a ranar Lahadi.
Sojoji da jiragen sama na kasuwanci suna kai kayan agaji da abinci.
Risa Kusuma, wata uwa mai shekaru 35 ta shaida wa Sky News: "Kowace minti daya, motar asibiti tana kawo gawawwaki.
Rashin ruwan sha mai tsabta yana da wuya.
An sace dukan ƙananan yara".
Jan Gelfand, darektan kungiyar Crus Red ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Jungiyar Crus Red ta Indonesia tana aiki a kowane lokaci don taimakawa wadanda suka tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya ƙara muni".
Shugaban kasar Indonesiya, Joko Widodo, ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin: "Ina rokon ku da ku duka da kuke aiki dare da rana don kammala dukkan ayyukan da suka shafi aikin kwashe mutane.
Shin kuna shirye?" CNN ta ruwaito.
Indonesia ta sake fuskantar wata girgizar kasa a wannan shekarar a Lombok, inda mutane fiye da 550 suka mutu.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Air Niugini ya ce yanzu an rasa mutum daya bayan hadarin da ya faru a tafkin
Kamfanin jiragen sama da ke gudanar da wani jirgin sama da ya yi hatsari a wani tafki a tekun Micronesia ya ce wani mutum ya bace, duk da cewa a baya sun ce fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun tsira daga jirgin da ya yi hatsari.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa, tun ranar Asabar da yamma, ba su sami fasinja ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin yankin, asibitoci da masu bincike don gano shi.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa nan da nan ba ga buƙatun ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekarunsu ko ƙasashensu.
Jirgin ruwan gida ya taimaka wajen ceton wasu fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin lokacin da jirgin ya fada cikin ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin sama na tsibirin Chuuk.
Hukumomi sun sanar a ranar Juma'a cewa an kai mutum bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce a ranar Asabar akwai wasu fasinjoji shida da ke asibiti kuma dukkansu suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san dalilin da ya sa jirgin ya fadi ba, kuma ba a san ainihin abin da ya faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da kuma rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka sun ce jirgin ya sauka a cikin tafkin saboda ba shi da isasshen hanyar da zai bi.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya bi hanyar jirgin sama.
Wani fasinja ɗan ƙasar Amirka mai suna Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin ya yi saurin sauka.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da sauran fasinjoji sun yi nasarar tafiya cikin ruwa a cikin belin jirgin zuwa tashoshin gaggawa na jirgin sama, wanda ke nutsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun razana kuma suka fara ihu, kuma ya sami rauni a kan kansa.
Rundunar Sojojin Ruwa ta Amurka ta ce ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a kusa da su don inganta tashar jiragen ruwa sun kuma taimaka wajen ceto tare da jirgin ruwa mai cike da iska don ɗaukar mutanen da abin ya shafa zuwa ga gaci kafin jirgin ya nutse kusan mita 30 a cikin ruwa.
Bayanai daga Cibiyar Tsaron Tsaro ta Aviation sun nuna cewa mutane 111 sun mutu a cikin haɗarin jirgin sama da aka yi rajista a PNG, amma Air Niugini ba ta da hannu a cikin waɗannan haɗarin.
